in a quantum trajectory. Despite not being the focus
of this letter, we emphasize this connection because feedback
and FPTs are actually conceptually very similar. Both require
monitoring of a stochastic quantity and performing (or not)
actions depending on its value. In the case of the FPT, the
action is to continue or cease the dynamics. In the case of
feedback, it is to modify the Liouvillian.
